        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4738",
        "content": "Days, that need borrow No part of their good morrow From a fore spent night of sorrow:",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4738_291945_000023_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4738/291945/4738_291945_000023_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4738",
        "content": "Days, that in spite Of darkness, by the light Of a clear mind are day all night.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4738_291945_000024_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4738/291945/4738_291945_000024_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4738",
        "content": "Life, that dares send A challenge to his end, And when it comes, say, \"Welcome friend.\"",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-4738_291945_000025_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/4738/291945/4738_291945_000025_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4738",
        "content": "I wish her store Of worth may leave her poor Of wishes; and I wish-no more.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
