        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-4738",
        "content": "Mine be a cot beside the hill; A bee hive's hum shall sooth my ear; A willowy brook that turns a mill, With many a fall shall linger near.",
        "style_prompt": "M_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "M",
